        <updateDate>2021-04-26T18:59:48Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>English Language Unity Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes English as the official language of the United States. It establishes a framework for implementation and enforcement, including by testing English as part of the naturalization process. </p>]]>
        </text>
